        <p>Mental Constructs is a Tool which allows you to record thoughts, ideas , facts , links. You can Upgrade them to Constructs and then Exhibit them.
          You can start BrainStorm sessions and map them to constructs. These wide variety of features should be understood well before they are actually used.
